news.title: China Evergrande gets court notice regarding unit's $280 million recovery claim
news.para: The proceedings brought by unit Jinbi Property Management Company are related to the enforcement of Evergrande Property Services' deposit pledge of about 13.4 billion yuan.

news.title: Toronto home prices fall in November; down nearly 19% from 2022 peak
news.para: The seasonally adjusted average home price fell 2.2% in November from October to C$1,104,062 ($815,769), marking the fourth decline in the last five months.

news.title: Shree Cement plans to bid in India's lithium auction: Source
news.para: The move would be Shree Cement's first venture into mining and it has contacted Australia-based mining experts to work out details such as the premium that it should quote in its bid, the source added.

news.title: Two unauthorised colonies, labour quarters razed in Ludhiana
news.para: ​​These included an illegal colony being established at Star Road, Lohara; labour quarters being established in Jaspal Bangar area and another illegal under construction colony on Sua road, Giaspura.

news.title: PNB Housing Finance expects overall loan book to touch Rs one lakh crore in 3-4 years
news.para: The company is betting aggressively on the affordable home loan segment. "We started the affordable housing business a year back, and in the last 11 months we have reached loan book of Rs 1,000 crore," said Girish Kousgi, MD & CEO of PNB Housing Finance.

news.title: Veenu Gupta appointed as new Rajasthan RERA chairperson
news.para: ​After assuming charge, she said that emphasis will be laid on effectively implementing the provisions of the RERA Act.

news.title: Ahmedabad civic body to offer property tax rebate for green roofs
news.para: The Ahmedabad Municipal Corporation (AMC) has prepared a ‘GreenBlueYellow Roof’ (GBY Roof) incentive scheme to encourage owners of independent houses, like a rowhouse, bungalow, or tenement, to adopt eco-friendly practices.

news.title: Haryana not taking orders to curb Aravali mining seriously: NGT
news.para: In its November 30 order, NGT observed that the state government had not disclosed any information on steps taken to stop illegal mining of the hills that are only barriers holding back expansion of desert-like conditions from Rajasthan towards north India.

news.title: Nashik civic body to revise lease rates of its properties
news.para: NMC officials said the government slashed the rates for properties given to social outfits from 8% of the Ready Reckoner (RR) rate to 0.5%, and lease rates for commercial properties from 8% of RR rate to 0.7%.

news.title: Property tax defaulters in Varanasi face legal proceedings
news.para: However, as soon as the proceedings were initiated against a hotel in Lahurabir locality, the defaulter paid the dues of Rs 6.25 lakh.

news.title: Enforcement directorate arrests Heera Constructions' MD in money laundering case
news.para: According to sources, Abdul Rasheed alias Heera Babu was produced at Prevention of Money Laundering Act (PMLA) court in Kochi on Tuesday. Rasheed has been sent to ED custody for four days till Friday.

news.title: Kolkata: Quick nod to building plans on plots up to seven cottahs from January 2024
news.para: According to a KMC official, necessary preparations are being made to make the new system user friendly before rolling it out.

news.title: Falsely named in duping case by Samir Kochhar & Varun Bangera: Architects
news.para: Kochhar and Bangera had filed a complaint with Andheri police on November 21 alleging that the architects had duped them of around Rs 1 crore paid as total token amount for one flat each in the under-construction Bandra (West) building.

news.title: WeWork appoints Claudio Hidalgo as COO
news.para: Hidalgo served as the company's COO Americas between June and November this year, and was COO Latin America from April 2020 to August 2022. He succeeds Anthony Yazbeck, who stepped down from his role in October.

news.title: Geo-tagging of properties mandatory to avail property tax exemption in Delhi: MCD
news.para: If any taxpayer fails to geo-tag their properties by 31 January, they will not be able to avail 10 per cent rebate on lump sum advance payment of tax in the next financial year by June 30, it said.

news.title: Oberoi Realty completes acquisition of 6.4 acres land in Thane for Rs 196 crore
news.para: In May 2023, the company had entered into a memorandum of understanding with NRB Bearings (NRB) for acquiring the lands located at Pokhran Road 2, Thane, Maharashtra, together with structures thereon.

news.title: IWG resumes dividends, eyes $1 billion in medium-term profit
news.para: Switzerland-headquartered IWG, which owns the Spaces and Regus brands, has said it is looking to acquire more of collapsed rival WeWork's sites on expectations of strong demand.

news.title: Dalmia Cement (Bharat) appoints Puneet Yadu Dalmia as MD & CEO
news.para: The board also approved the appointment of Mahendra Singhi as strategic advisor to managing director & CEO with effect from December 9, 2023. Singhi will also act as non-executive non-independent director of Dalmia Cement (Bharat).
